description: High speed wireless connectivity on your desktop or notebook is at your fingertips with this Etekcity dual antenna wireless network adapter for 802.11 b/g/n wireless networks.Just follow the simple steps in the quick start guide and you will be connected to your 802.11b/g/n network in no time! Because this adapter comes with two antennas,it provides far greater signal strength than a single antenna model. It is compatible with almost all laptops, desktop computers, PCs, and Macs. This Wireless USB Adapter gives you the flexibility to install wireless networks on your PC or notebook wherever is most convenient for you, without the cost of running network cables.Description:1.Supports Windows XP/Vista/7/8,Linux,Mac.2.Etekcity Long-distance USB WiFi Adapters for 802.11b/g/n wireless networks.3.With TWO 6dBi antennas which provides stronger signal for single antenna.4.It is compatible with almost all laptops and desktop, PCs and Macs.5.It has a stunning 1000mw output power. So if you are looking for a device to connect to an outdoor 2.4 GHz antenna, such as on a boat or an RV, this is a perfect solution.6.This Wireless USB Adapter gives you the flexibility to install the PC or notebook in the most convenient location available,without the cost of running network cables.7.Its auto-sensing capability allows high packet transfer up to 300Mbps for maximum throughput.8.Or dynamic range shifting to lower speeds due to distance or operating limitations in an environment with a lot of electromagnetic interference.Package includes:1x WiFi USB Adapter1x Driver CD1x Quick Start Guide1x USB Cable2x 6DBI Antenna
title: Etekcity® USB Wireless Wi-Fi Network Adapter with Dual 6 dBi Antennas - 802.11 B/G/N 300Mbps
